[[Tugna:HRDiagram.png|thumb|350px|23,000 seg telmas yemgaraden n yitran i d-yettbinen deg twenɣa-ayi. Asuneɣ yemmal-d d akken tilmas n yitran ṭṭafarent tameknut imalen deg telɣa yuzdawen seg teɣmert tazelmaṭ tafellayt (itran mellulen, izeqqlen s waṭas) ɣer teɣmert tayeffust taddayt (itran ur nzeqqel ara s waṭas), tagrawt-a tettwasemma s '''welkem agejdan'''. Akken i yella uẓuni n [[agezlan amellal|iwezlanen imellalen]], akken i yella sufell n welkem tagrawt n [[azuncafcal|yizuncafcalen]] (''subgiants''), d tegrawt n yicafcalen (''giants''), d [[afelcafcal|yifelcafcalen]] (''supergiants'') igebren seg - s unect n yisem-is - itran meqqren s waṭas s wassaɣ ɣer [[takura tanafukt|tkura tanafukt]]. Ma d [[tafukt]] tella deg tlemmast n welkem agejdan d itri yegdan 1 n tkura tanafukt, d [[Azal amagdez|wazal amagdez]] yegdan 4,8, d umatar n yini 0.66 (B-V color index) d [[taẓɣelt|teẓɣelt]] 5.780 C d telmest n [[Aggwa|waylal]] G2.]]

'''Alkam agejdan''' di [[Tasnallunt|tesnallunt]] d azlem uddinan n [[itri|yitran]] issiliɣ-d azal n 80% seg yitran yemgaraden deg umeɣrad, tessegraw-it-id yiwet n twenɣa ,i wakken ad t-ittessesmel s unect n yini d tedwast n [[Asfijjej (tasnallunt)|usfijjej]]. Itran n welkem agejdan ttwassnen s akken [[tafasa]] n usfijjej-nsen d tin i d-yekkan seg tsedmirt n  [[tazrart pṛutun-pṛutun|wezday aɣisan n uhidṛujin]] deg wul n yitri, dɣa anecta iga d snat n tsedmirin n wezday aɣisan i d-igellun s [[Hilyum|uhilyum].

Tawenɣa issegrawen ger n tkura n yitri d yini n yini [[aggwa|waylal-is]] d tedwast n usfijjej-is tettwasemma s [[Ameskan n Hertzsprung–Russell|usesmel n Hertzsprung–Russell]], ma d tagrawt n yitran n ubaggus-a di twenɣa-ayi tettwasemma s '''welkem agejdan''', acku tessiliɣ-d azal n 80% seg telmas n yitran yellan deg umeɣrad. Ma d isesmilen n yitran yeffɣen seg ubaggus-a agejdan ssesmilen-d 20% seg yitran n umeɣrad, dɣa ttemsegrawen-d di twenɣa ɣef sin n yibaggusen niḍen, yerna iglamen-nsen mgaraden s waṭas ɣef yiglamen n yitran n welkem agejdan, acku asufeɣ-nsen d ufares-nsen i tfasa yettuɣal ɣer tsedmirin niḍen anagar [[azday aɣisan]] n [[Hidṛujin|uhidṛujin]] i d-igellun s uhilyum.

